Class ParetoDominanceComparator

java.lang.Object
org.moeaframework.core.comparator.ChainedComparator
org.moeaframework.core.comparator.ParetoDominanceComparator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, DominanceComparator
public class ParetoDominanceComparator extends ChainedComparator implements Serializable
Compares two solutions using aggregate constraint violation and the Pareto dominance relation as originally proposed by Kalyanmoy Deb.

References:

  1. Deb, K., "An Efficient Constraint Handling Method for Genetic Algorithms." Computer Methods in Applied Mechanics and Engineering, pp. 311--338, 1998.
